this is a iot project "smart wacth" 
which can receive voice command from an android app
to send tweets, display weather, and do gesture recognition,
the code is for the server side. 

server.py receives data and put data into MongoDB

sk.py reads data from MongoDB and trains the model 

clf is the trained multiclass svc model

wse.py receives requests from MCU to send tweets, 
collect weather imformation and do gesture regconigtion,
and send back response to MCU to display the information on oled
